      "raw_text": "WENATCHEE, Wash. Sept. IL.\nGreat Northern railway passen-\nger trains will be running through\nthe Cascade tunnel before January\n1 and probably by December l.,\ndrawn by electric locomotives. The\nconstruction department is rushing\nthe finishing of one of the largest\nundertakings of it's kind ever at\ntempted in the west, and when the\njob is done the Great Northern will\nbe the first of the northern lines to\noperate passenger trains by cleo\ntricity over any considerable por-\nton of it's road."
    }
